Working with Vim Editor
-----------------------

Vim (Vi improved) Its a terminal based text-editor used to 
. Edit Config files on servers
. Write scripts
. Debug logs
. Work over ssh (no GUI)

Vim has 3 main modes

Mode     purpose
Normal   Navigation+commands
Insert   Typing text
Command  Save, Quit, Actions

Mode flow

Normal -> (i) -> Instert -> (Esc) -> Normal -> (:) -> Command

Basic Commands:

# Open file
vim <file_name>

# Insert text 
(i)

# Exit Insert Mode
(Esc)

# Save and Quit
:wq

# Quit without saving
:q!

