Navigation key Shortcuts

h   =  Left
l   =  Right
j   =  Go Down
k   =  Go Up

Word Movement
w   =  Next word
b   =  Previous word

Line Movement
0   =  Start of the line
$   =  end of the line

Jump
gg  = top of the file
G   = bottom of the file

Editing 
dd  =  Delete line
x   =  Delete character

Copy & Paste
yy  =  Copy line
p   =  Paste

Search
/error
n -> Next match
N -> Previous match

